name: Fish Seized From a Pelican's Mouth
desc: A fish you managed to retrieve from the mouth of a pelican at the Qiaoying Village docks. It seems to be an item that other creatures treasure greatly, so you might be able to make amends for a certain loss from a certain time by returning this to the daily feeding vessel of certain animals...
